# Auto ISP Billing huntgroups (s36b7)
# Dispatches NAS-Port-Type to policy buckets so admins can write
# per-method policies (throttling, ACLs, authorize filters).
#
# These three Huntgroup names match the auth_type values used by our
# CompanySettings + admin_users UI.
isp-pppoe-session    NAS-Port-Type == Virtual
isp-hotspot-session  NAS-Port-Type == Wireless-802.11
isp-ethernet-session NAS-Port-Type == Ethernet
